2ebebdea-86c5-42e9-99c3-f5dce65575b9.title: Brand
2ebebdea-86c5-42e9-99c3-f5dce65575b9.story: Once a tribesman of the icy Freljord named Kegan Rodhe, the creature known as Brand is a lesson in the temptation of greater power.

dc03a86c-46b6-49af-902f-5bf20e802dff.title: Swain
dc03a86c-46b6-49af-902f-5bf20e802dff.story: Born into a patrician family, one of many to exist since the first walls were raised around Noxus, Jericho Swain seemed destined for a life of privilege.
